				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10682652/scp-4533#post-4672860</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 01 Jun 2020 16:59:23 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Irina Bougainvillea</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>6048746</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This creeps me out, not only by the nature of the SCP, but also by hindering something deeper.</p> <p>The problem with letting big companies fiddle with your personal data online or offline - or in this case letting an anomaly related to consumption and commercial fiddle with your body, yourself - for some profit is that, is it worth exchanging at all?</p> <p>Poor those affected people :((</p> <p>Love the creativity. Easy +1, and I would say this is underrated.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
